M_iX_i=\int_0^{L_i} x_i\rho_i\,\mathrm dx_i
X=\frac{\int_0^{L_1} x_1\rho_1\,\mathrm dx_1 + \int_0^{L_2} x_2\rho_2\,\mathrm dx_2 + \cdots}{M_1+M_2+\cdots}.
